{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674970/extras/DSM_616x353.gif?t=1733371746\" />In Devil Slot Machine, you need to battle demons incarnated as pinballs on a slot machine. Purchase various chips to build a strong defense. However, remember that demons are always cunning, so be prepared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>The  demo now fully supports English, and the main game's English version is nearing completion. Welcome to add Devil Slot Machine to your wishlist!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Life is Precious</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After each battle, you can purchase chips in the shop and place them on the battlefield. You can also upgrade the shop, refresh goods to find desirable chips, but all of this consumes your precious life points. Completing levels will reward you with life points, and there are many chips that restore life points waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674970/extras/\u751f\u547d\u53ef\u8d35.gif?t=1733371746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Construct Your Build</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chips have various abilities: pirates excel at producing life points, flower fairies are skilled at group combat, and different chip systems can create magical synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674970/extras/\u7ec4\u5efa\u6784\u7b51.gif?t=1733371746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Powerful Talents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After passing specific wave-based levels, you can choose one of four different talents, each with powerful abilities, some of which can even affect the gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674970/extras/\u65b0-\u89d2\u8272-en.gif?t=1733371746\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiple Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are four characters to choose from, each with unique attack styles and gameplay features. Pick the character that suits you best and defeat the devils!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674970/extras/\u5207\u6362\u89d2\u8272.gif?t=1733371746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bullet Hell</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once charged, chips can fire bullets to attack demons. Meanwhile, the demons have prepared various types of bullets  for you as well. You must deftly move and survive in this relentless bullet hell! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674970/extras/\u5f39\u5e55\u65f6\u95f4.gif?t=1733371746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roguelike pinball tower defense experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tower deck building</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 selectable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 unique stages </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Screen-filling dazzling bullet patterns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro dark pixel art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loads of pinballs!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Angel Descends","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2674970/754dfb1581543dd3aaec8a7636fbec8624c8d58f.jpg"},{"name":"Bomb!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2674970/fd94a7016a80b0dde1f28d430fd012d03c069ea0.jpg"},{"name":"I Am the Bone of My Sword","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2674970/e461ef637988d50922c9b478db495791c48a3cb3.jpg"},{"name":"First Win","path":"https:/